EADS Chief Seeks Veto Power on Hostile Takeovers, Focus Reports

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-05-29T12:10:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/eads-chief-seeks-veto-power-on-hostile-takeovers-focus-reports.html
European Aeronautic, Defence & Space
Co. should provide for a “veto right” to guard against hostile
takeovers,  Focus  magazine quoted Chief Executive Officer  Louis Gallois  as saying.  Aerospace is an industry of national interest and there are
ways to give the French and German governments appropriate
influence, the magazine cited Gallois as saying in a preview of
an interview e-mailed today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
